OL,3,CThe mum helping to save hundreds of
OL,4,Clives in son's memory
OL,6,FITV Granada Reports correspondent Tim
OL,7,FScott has been speaking to Deborah
OL,8,FDixon whose son died as a result of a
OL,9,Fundiagnosed heart condition.
OL,11,FA mother who has helped save hundreds
OL,12,Fof lives by fundraising for heart
OL,13,Fscans for young people after the
OL,14,Fsudden death of her son has met a
OL,15,Fwoman who owes her life to her hard
OL,16,Fwork.
OL,18,FAaron Dixon died in 2011 of an
OL,19,Fundiagnosed heart condition at his
OL,20,Fhome, in Tarporley in Cheshire, at the
OL,21,Fage of 23.
