OL,3,CThe mum helping to save hundreds of
OL,4,Clives in son's memory
OL,6,FThe heart scans, open to anyone aged
OL,7,F14 to 35, have saved hundreds of
OL,8,Flives, including beautician Georgia
OL,9,FBriscall who needed keyhole surgery
OL,10,Fafter a screening picked up an atrial
OL,11,Fseptal defect.
OL,13,F"They (doctors) said that the blood is
OL,14,Fpumping around the wrong way", Georgia
OL,15,Fexplains. "They said that is why
OL,16,Fyou're feeling tired. They said my
OL,17,Fheart was doing the opposite of what
OL,18,Fit should do."
